  "texts": [
    "Ablation Experiments on higher-Order Topological Structures and higher-Order Node Information.",
    "network datasets, we have demonstrated the effectiveness of our model in node classification tasks.",
    "A series of ablation studies have shown that the performance of TWC-GNN is significantly influenced by the integration of higher-order topological structures and higher-order node information.",
    "In conclusion, our findings highlight the importance of higher-order structural information in directed networks, providing a strong foundation for future research in complex graph-based learning tasks.",
    "The proposed TWC-GNN model offers a promising approach for extracting and leveraging global and local graph features, enabling more accurate and efficient node classification in directed networks."
  ]
}